                    <title>The Washington Post Also Misreported CNN’s False WikiLeaks Story</title>
                <?php include_once 'Elemental/header.php'; ?><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><br><br><h5> This article is reformatted from originally published at <a href="https://caityjohnstone.medium.com/the-washington-post-also-misreported-cnns-false-wikileaks-story-5c3f38365f05"><strong>TDS(Towards Data Science)</strong></a></h5></br><h5> <a href="https://medium.com/?source=post_page-----5c3f38365f05--------------------------------">Author : Caitlin Johnstone</a> </h5></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content4 cid-tt5SM2WLsM" id="content4-2" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
            <div class="container">
